OL,3,CChild dies in tragic pond incident at
OL,4,Cgolf course
OL,6,FA child has died following an incident
OL,7,Fat a golf course pond in Doncaster,
OL,8,Fpolice say.
OL,10,FThe child, was discovered in the pond
OL,11,Fat Owston Hall golf course after being
OL,12,Freported missing on Monday.
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire Police were alerted to
OL,15,Freports of a missing child from the
OL,16,FSkellow area shortly before 10am on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
