OL,3,CChild dies in tragic pond incident at
OL,4,Cgolf course
OL,6,FThe force deployed drones and an
OL,7,Faircraft to find them, and shortly
OL,8,Fafter discovered them in a pond at the
OL,9,Fcourse.
OL,11,FA police spokesperson said: "Following
OL,12,Fan extensive search, the child was
OL,13,Flocated in a pond on Owston Hall golf
OL,14,Fcourse.
OL,16,F"Sadly, despite the best efforts of
OL,17,Femergency services colleagues, they
OL,18,Fwere pronounced deceased.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
